| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0548 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6cb540d3-f87d-5d39-b997-8ea03a69d790"
